*Network*
-> a collection of connected devices that facilitate communication and data transimission.

*Internet*
-> global network of interconnected computer networks (basically the same definition of 'network' but on a larger scale.

*Advanced Research Projects Agency Network (ARPANET)*
-> the first wide-area packet-switched network with distributed control and one of the first computer networks to implement the TCP/IP protocol suite
